@(B.42 = 42-61) @wDN{An} …… favourable day …… holy ……. He has a righteous crown, long-lasting divine powers and a royal sceptre. @wDN{Enlil} has decreed lordship for his beloved one, as his destiny, and has created with magnificent grandeur the qualities of a warrior. @wDN{Enki}, renewing abundance and days of splendour, …… the @wWN{Tigris} and @wWN{Euphrates} in their wide flooding. @wDN{Nintur}, who causes human seed to propagate and brings living beings into existence, …… cities and crowded places, all the numerous people together. @wDN{Nanna}, the …… light, confirming the divine plans, new moon of eternal fame, light which goes towards the earth, has given authority (?) to my @wRN{Ibbi-@wDN{Suen}}, foremost among princes, over the south and the uplands as far as the outer limits of heaven and earth. @wDN{Utu} has produced justice and propriety for @wRN{Ibbi-@wDN{Suen}} the augustly powerful, strong among warriors, unsurpassed in his youthfulness, overthrowing the enemy lands, finding the right decisions and giving advice to the people. The good lady @wDN{Ninirigal}, mother of @wSN{Kulaba}, …… prayer and supplication ……, …… lady with an august name ……. …… long life.

